---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout lang="en" title="Privacy Policy — SyncAgency" description="SyncAgency Privacy Policy and personal data protection." pageKey="crm">
  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 120px auto; padding: 0 24px 120px;">
    <style>
      .legal-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .legal-title { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 40px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text-primary, #F2F2F2); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .legal-date { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-text-muted, #737373); margin-bottom: 56px; }
      .legal-intro { font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-text-secondary, #999); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 56px; }
      .legal-section { margin-bottom: 44px; }
      .legal-section-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-primary, #F2F2F2); margin-bottom: 14px; }
      .legal-section p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-text-secondary, #999); line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 12px; }
      .legal-section ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 8px 0 12px; }
      .legal-section li { font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-text-secondary, #999); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 6px; }
      .legal-section strong { color: var(--color-text-primary, #F2F2F2); font-weight: 600; }
      .legal-section a { color: var(--color-primary, #8AA5FF); text-decoration: none; }
      .legal-section a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
      .legal-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin: 0 0 44px; }
    </style>

    <p class="legal-eyebrow">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="legal-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-date">Last updated: November 30, 2025</p>

    <p class="legal-intro">Welcome to <strong>SyncAgency</strong>. This Privacy Policy is intended to help you understand what information we collect, why we collect it, and how you can update, manage, export, and delete your information when you use our services.</p>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">1. Data Controller</h2>
      <p>The processing of personal data carried out on the site <a href="https://www.syncagency.fr">https://www.syncagency.fr</a> and the associated application is under the responsibility of:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Legal name:</strong> SyncAgency LLC</li>
        <li><strong>Managing member:</strong> Lucas Provenzano (Sole Member)</li>
        <li><strong>EIN (Employer Identification Number):</strong> 35-2955550</li>
        <li><strong>Registered office:</strong> 1209 Mountain Rd Pl NE Ste H, Albuquerque, NM 87110, United States</li>
        <li><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@syncagency.fr">contact@syncagency.fr</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">2. Data Collected</h2>
      <p>In the context of using our software solution (SaaS), we may collect the following data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Identification data:</strong> Last name, first name, agency name, email address, phone number.</li>
        <li><strong>Billing and payment data:</strong> Transaction history, billing address (sensitive credit card information is processed and secured directly by our PCI-DSS certified payment partner and does not pass through our servers).</li>
        <li><strong>Technical connection data:</strong> IP address, connection logs, browser type, to ensure infrastructure security.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
      <p>Your data is strictly used for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Creating and managing your user account on our CRM.</li>
        <li>Providing our communication and audience management services.</li>
        <li>Managing billing, payments, and accounting.</li>
        <li>Customer support and technical issue resolution.</li>
        <li>Fraud prevention and compliance with our legal obligations (notably for anti-money-laundering purposes).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">4. Data Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
      <p>Your data is never resold for commercial purposes. It may only be shared with our strict subcontractors for the delivery of the service:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Our secure hosting providers.</li>
        <li>Our payment partners (banking gateways and acquirers) for the secure processing of financial transactions.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your data for the strict duration of use of our services. In the event of deletion of your account, your identification and billing data is retained for the legally required period (generally 7 years for fiscal and accounting obligations) before being permanently erased.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">6. Data Security</h2>
      <p>SyncAgency implements enhanced technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration (encryption of communications via SSL/TLS, restricted access to databases).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">7. Your Rights (GDPR Compliance)</h2>
      <p>In accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Right of access and rectification.</li>
        <li>Right to erasure (right to be forgotten).</li>
        <li>Right to restriction of processing.</li>
        <li>Right to data portability.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, you may contact us at the following address: <a href="mailto:contact@syncagency.fr">contact@syncagency.fr</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">8. Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time in order to keep it compliant with legal developments. The version in force is the one accessible online on this page.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2 class="legal-section-title">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or the management of your data, please contact us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@syncagency.fr">contact@syncagency.fr</a></li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.syncagency.fr">www.syncagency.fr</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
